OL,3,CParaglider narrowly escapes death
OL,4,Cafter plane rips through her parachute
OL,6,FA paraglider narrowly escaped death
OL,7,Fwhen an aircraft ripped through her
OL,8,Fparachute, sending her tumbling
OL,9,Fthrough the air.
OL,11,FSabrina, 44, had launched from the
OL,12,FSchmittenhohe mountain near Zell am
OL,13,FSee, in the Austrian state of
OL,14,FSalzburg, on May 23, when a man flying
OL,15,Fa single-engine light aircraft Cessna
OL,16,F172 tore apart her equipment.
OL,26,@tD@Kxw
