PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779829869
OL,3,CParaglider narrowly escapes death
OL,4,Cafter plane rips through her parachute
OL,6,FIn a video of the incident, the
OL,7,Faircraft flies from behind her,
OL,8,Ftearing the parachute in two and
OL,9,Fcausing her to hurtle towards the
OL,10,Fground.
OL,12,FFortunately, Sabrina was able to
OL,13,Fquickly deploy her reserve parachute,
OL,14,Fand after a difficult journey down,
OL,15,Fspinning through the air, she landed
OL,16,Fsafely in the forest.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
