FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779829869
OL,3,CParaglider narrowly escapes death
OL,4,Cafter plane rips through her parachute
OL,6,FShe was then airlifted by a police
OL,7,Fhelicopter to Zell am See Airport, but
OL,8,Fshe only sustained minor injuries -
OL,9,Fbruises and contusions - from the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FThe pilot also escaped unharmed.
OL,14,FPosting the video on Instagram,
OL,15,FSabrina wrote in the caption: "I
OL,16,Factually still can't believe that I'm
OL,17,Fsitting here typing this and apart
OL,18,Ffrom a few nasty bruises and bruises
OL,19,Fall around, nothing really happened."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
