PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779829869
OL,3,CParaglider narrowly escapes death
OL,4,Cafter plane rips through her parachute
OL,6,FThe incident has been reported to
OL,7,FAustro Control, the air navigation
OL,8,Fservices provider for Austria, and
OL,9,Fpolice have filed a charge of causing
OL,10,Fbodily injury through negligence
OL,11,Fagainst the pilot.
OL,13,FAccording to his own statement, the
OL,14,Fpilot was unable to avoid the
OL,15,Fcollision in time during the accident,
OL,16,Fthe police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
