PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779829869
OL,3,CParaglider narrowly escapes death
OL,4,Cafter plane rips through her parachute
OL,6,F"It's just an airfield in the
OL,7,Fparaglider, and also the gliders and
OL,8,Fmotor pilots are doing their rounds,"
OL,9,FSabrina wrote on Instagram after her
OL,10,Fvideo went viral.
OL,12,F"There are rules and accidents happen
OL,13,Fanyway. Maybe this will help everyone
OL,14,Ffly a little more attentively.
OL,16,F"I understand that a paraglider, just
OL,17,Flike a glider for us, is often
OL,18,Fdifficult to see - even though we are
OL,19,Fbeautifully colourful."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
